Rated Bullet game (https://lichess.org/J7spIVlt) B01 2023.08.28
B01 Scandinavian, Pytel-Wade variation

1.e4 d5 2.exd5 Qxd5 3.Nc3 Qd6 4.Nf3 Nf6 5.d4 a6 B01 Scandinavian Defense: Bronstein Variation 6.g3 Nc6 7.Bf4 Qb4 8.Rb1 Bg4 9.Bg2 O-O-O 10.d5 e5 11.Bd2 e4 12.Ne2 exf3 13.Bxb4 fxg2 14.Rg1 Nxb4 15.f3 Rxd5 16.Qc1 Bxf3 17.Kf2 Bh5 18.Nf4 Ne4+ 19.Kxg2 Rd2+ 20.Kh3 Nf2+ 21.Kh4 Be7+ 22.Kxh5 g6+ 23.Kh6 Ng4+ 24.Kg7 Bf6+ 25.Kxf7 Rd7+ 26.Ke6 Re8# Black wins by checkmate.
